{"tid":58806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人大代表專強姦處女 4名幼齒受害","createTime":"2016-12-29T06:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:49:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8867df9aec304db960ae0920a79e0078a834e78f","tid":58806,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"中國內蒙古滿洲里人大代表石學和，被指控透過仲介， <br />\n專找處女來性侵，自今年5月以來至少有4名女中學生受害。 <br />\n<br />\n據中國《新浪網》與《閩南網》報導，有一名13歲女學生胡雲(化名)， <br />\n在過去2個月被3人性侵6次，自此之後變了一個人， <br />\n並被醫師診斷患上「精神障礙」，輟學在家，甚至一度企圖自殺， <br />\n案件因此被傳開。跟胡雲有相同遭遇的，還有3名國中女生。 <br />\n據了解，胡雲與另一女生吳月(化名)，皆遭到暴力威脅賣淫， <br />\n她們首次接客時均為處女之身，並被安排到酒店與石學和發生關係。 <br />\n<br />\n胡雲受不了變成石學和的性奴，企圖尋短，幸好同學及時發現， <br />\n胡雲才撿回一命，案件也因此爆發開來，警方也開始進行調查。 <br />\n一名仲介人王紅就說，石學和要求的不僅是處女，還要功課好， <br />\n據悉石學和在與女孩發生性關係過程中，沒有戴保險套。 <br />\n石男也曾經要花60萬元人民幣(約新台幣300萬元)與胡家私了， <br />\n但遭到家屬拒絕。受害女學生形容，石學和穿西裝、白襯衫， <br />\n有大肚，頭髮往後梳，長得很醜。 <br />\n<br />\n事件越滾越大，上月24日滿洲里市人大常委會決定接受 <br />\n石學和辭去人大代表職務，不過家屬也不滿， <br />\n調查單位始終不肯公布調查進度。（施旖婕／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"33ba84f633c27352a2b122f9f9b6efb49112a518","tid":58806,"uid":5293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfafe67b56219178f0ccf68898e8e37fac32b4b","tid":58806,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4730fd0265cd8568795b075c899d8fcafe5dc966","tid":58806,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"江山都是我們黨的，玩幾個女孩算什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97edc44f8e50e1d5b06e51be5b07fcc8ccdea207","tid":58806,"uid":634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbac700f6f22495afe1d4860ea1bb7311bd7b37e","tid":58806,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ca6bcdea7e2cc64b02c89bf0971a08573c56036","tid":58806,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a10ea96e91abc669bf2e552589df15de3194d97b","tid":58806,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:52:19.000Z","msg":"不愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7293ec0a5d8c949847f96f389e001947a4b6eefa","tid":58806,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:01:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"316caf03586442df149b05c34681e37f50ca3932","tid":58806,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:42:36.000Z","msg":"女人都係黨"},{"pid":"a88fb7c296453e2852500757f08050eb56dc7ba9","tid":58806,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>江山都是我們黨的，玩幾個女孩算什麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n處女都是黨的資產"},{"pid":"0677b6aae4dcc457276bf8dee5de041d819699ee","tid":58806,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">施旖婕</span></span></blockquote>"}]}